display="inline"><![CDATA[i\in \mathbb {N}]]></fr:tex> to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[e{\mathopen {}\left (i\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> if <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[e{\mathopen {}\left (i\right )\mathclose {}}\in  S]]></fr:tex> and to <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex> otherwise.</fr:p>
